<h1>ThemeToggle</h1>
<p>Dark/light mode toggle button that persists the user preference to <code>localStorage</code>.</p>

<h2 id="automatic_inclusion">// automatic_inclusion</h2>
<p><code>ThemeToggle</code> is fully self-contained and included automatically by <code>DocSite</code> in the top bar. You do not need to add it manually.</p>

<h2 id="standalone_usage">// standalone_usage</h2>
<p>If you need <code>ThemeToggle</code> outside of <code>DocSite</code>, you can render it directly anywhere in the component tree.</p>

<CodeBlock Files="@_usage" Language="razor" />

@code {
    private static readonly Dictionary<string, string> _usage = new()
    {
        ["MyPage.razor"] = "<ThemeToggle />",
    };
}
